# Cloudflare Pages security headers template
# Shipped by the `security-headers` bundle in stharrold-templates v8.9.
#
# This is a conservative baseline distilled from running synavistra.ai
# for 6+ months with three separate security-review bots pointing out
# issues. Customize the route-specific overrides for your own app;
# leave the /* defaults alone unless you know what you're breaking.
#
# See bundles/security-headers/README.md for the full ~12 gotchas
# documented during the synavistra session on 2026-04-05.

# Baseline — applies to every page unless overridden below
/*
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), microphone=(), camera=()
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains; preload
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; script-src 'self'; img-src 'self' data:; font-src 'self'; frame-ancestors 'none'; form-action 'self'

# Example: route that needs DuckDB-WASM / ONNX Runtime Web / WebGPU
# (uncomment and adapt if you ship in-browser inference)
#
# Requires COOP/COEP for SharedArrayBuffer, a relaxed CSP that allows
# wasm-unsafe-eval + unsafe-eval (Emscripten glue uses dynamic code
# execution), and cdn.jsdelivr.net in script-src/worker-src (DuckDB's
# Worker JS and WASM binary can't be fully vendored -- see the bundle
# README for the upstream reasons).
#
# /*/showcases/my-wasm-app*
#   Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; script-src 'self' 'wasm-unsafe-eval' 'unsafe-eval' https://cdn.jsdelivr.net; connect-src 'self' https://models.example.com https://cdn.jsdelivr.net; img-src 'self' data:; font-src 'self'; worker-src 'self' blob: https://cdn.jsdelivr.net; frame-ancestors 'none'; form-action 'self'
#   Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
#   Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: credentialless

# Cache headers for static assets
/*.html
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=3600, must-revalidate

/
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=3600, must-revalidate

/assets/css/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable

/assets/js/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable

/assets/fonts/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable

/assets/images/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable
